1
00:00:54,200 --> 00:00:54,840
These

2
00:00:56,640 --> 00:00:59,440
are medicinal foods made from top-grade elixirs.

3
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:01,040
They replenish blood and qi

4
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,520
and cleanse the muscles and marrow.

5
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,160
They were specially made for you.

6
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,420
So you should eat more.

7
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:08,160
Could these be poisoned?

8
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:12,090
Don't be so nervous.

9
00:01:12,600 --> 00:01:13,930
This is Tiandao Palace.

10
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:15,800
For your Likong Clan in this world,

11
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:17,200
this is the safest place.

12
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:21,840
The way we brought you back this time

13
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,180
was indeed a bit rough.

14
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:24,130
However,

15
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,820
that was because you ignored our summons

16
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,240
and disregarded the sect.

17
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:29,280
We had no choice

18
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,640
but to resort to this.

19
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,360
You mean,

20
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:35,640
if you call me back,

21
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:36,700
I have to come back,

22
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:37,960
and I can't resist?

23
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:42,039
It is extremely dangerous for your Likong Clan out there.

24
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:43,280
We summoned you back

25
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:45,400
to protect your safety.

26
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:46,240
Exactly.

27
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,280
Why can't

28
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,200
you understand?

29
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,440
Then,

30
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,880
what if I have someone to protect me?

31
00:01:57,880 --> 00:01:59,080
Can't I still refuse?

32
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,840
In this world,

33
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,480
is there any sect

34
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:05,000
safer than our Tiandao Palace?

35
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:09,860
It seems you truly don't know the dangers of this world.

36
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:11,240
Forcing you to return

37
00:02:11,720 --> 00:02:13,520
was indeed the right thing to do.

38
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,740
Stay here for a few days first.

39
00:02:16,440 --> 00:02:18,640
Once the Likong Clan makes room for you,

40
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:20,380
I will come and take you there.

41
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,000
Exactly.

42
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:37,329
Are they trying to imprison me?

43
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,120
What should I do to escape?

44
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,440
Is this Tiandao Palace?

45
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,840
It's truly magnificent.

46
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,610
Shouldn't we discuss how to get in?

47
00:02:55,880 --> 00:02:56,340
Wuzhou,

48
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,600
let's go to the other side

49
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:58,400
and sneak in.

50
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:02,120
We can't go in with the Demon Lord.

51
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,280
Otherwise, our identities will be hard to explain.

52
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,800
But if the Demon Lord breaks in,

53
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:08,000
he will definitely attract most of the attention.

54
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,860
This is the best way for us to secretly rescue Danyu.

55
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:11,800
Yes,

56
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,560
Xiaoxue.

57
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,200
You are right.

58
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:13,730
Let's go.

59
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:28,520
Lanqi Moyuan.

60
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:33,050
Escaping the seal is one thing.

61
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,720
Instead of hiding in secret,

62
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,050
you dare to come to Tiandao Palace.

63
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:38,880
Aren't you afraid

64
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:40,680
that just like twenty years ago,

65
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,010
you'll be sealed again?

66
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:44,960
What?

67
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,440
Are you worried about my safety?

68
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,200
Luo Chunyi,

69
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:51,340
you even thought about how I should survive.

70
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,960
Who's worried about you?

71
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,540
I'm just afraid

72
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:57,050
you won't be able to die in Tiandao Palace.

73
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:00,410
You don't need to worry about that.

74
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,210
This Tiandao Palace

75
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,860
can't keep me here.

76
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,640
Then let's try.

77
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,520
All disciples, take your positions.

78
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:14,320
Set up the Demon Refining Array!

79
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:17,450
Whoever can hurt the Demon King

80
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,529
will receive double sect rewards!

81
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:26,960
Yiyi.

82
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,640
He really came to save me.

83
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,640
He really came.

84
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:31,000
I knew it.

85
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:32,080
He is different

86
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,200
from other demons.

87
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,280
The third time.

88
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:06,250
This is the third time you stood in front of me.

89
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:09,450
I couldn't do anything for you before.

90
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:10,640
So,

91
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,420
it's my turn this time.

92
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,880
I need to know

93
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:16,320
why you hate the human race so much,

94
00:06:16,760 --> 00:06:18,440
yet still show compassion.

95
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,960
I will help you.

96
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:22,520
Lanqi Moyuan's

97
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:24,680
demonic power is growing daily.

98
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:27,920
He can already easily suppress the Netherworld.

99
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:29,720
The demonic seal on him

100
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,920
has almost completely faded.

101
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,920
If this continues,

102
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,200
I'm afraid the human race

103
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:38,330
will have a hard time controlling him.

104
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,500
No, Palace Master.

105
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,320
A'yuan

106
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:42,450
is absolutely loyal to the human race.

107
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,240
It is him

108
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,280
who for so many years

109
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:47,740
has suppressed those Netherworld demons without complaint.

110
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:48,400
A'yuan

111
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:50,600
will never betray the human race.

112
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,900
He's a human-demon hybrid picked up from Lanqi.

113
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,720
You expect him to be loyal to the human race?

114
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,850
That's a bit too wishful thinking.

115
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,440
Those not of our kind

116
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:02,760
will surely have different loyalties.

117
00:07:02,760 --> 00:07:03,840
Our Tiandao Palace

118
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,320
cannot take that bet.

119
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,020
Palace Master.

120
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:13,080
We will discuss this no further.

121
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:15,760
Palace...

122
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:51,980
Palace Master.

123
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,840
The blood of these Likong people

124
00:07:53,840 --> 00:07:54,900
is not pure enough.

125
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:57,480
It is fine for suppressing ordinary demons,

126
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,409
but Lanqi Moyuan

127
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,840
has become the Demon Lord.

128
00:07:59,840 --> 00:08:00,440
I am afraid

129
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,240
it can no longer suppress him.

130
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,400
Where is Qinglan?

131
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,650
Still in the Nursery Pavilion.

132
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:08,120
If Li Qinglan provides blood,

133
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,080
I am afraid his origin

134
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:10,930
and lifespan

135
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,760
will suffer further damage.

136
00:08:14,080 --> 00:08:17,000
We only have this last pureblood left.

137
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,260
Then just make up the numbers.

138
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,460
Palace Master,

139
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:22,640
over the years, to suppress the Netherworld,

140
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,500
the Likong clan

141
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,120
has lost more than half of its people.

142
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,240
More than half?

143
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:29,720
Ever since the Likong clan had their blood corrupted by the Nether Demon,

144
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,580
the entire clan

145
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:32,080
of 43,000 people

146
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:35,570
has come under the protection of our Tiandao Palace.

147
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,600
Nowadays,

148
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:39,039
not only has their population not increased,

149
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:40,900
but they have lost more than half.

150
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:43,039
Isn't this too harsh on them?

151
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,800
What you are saying now

152
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,040
is meaningless.

153
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:50,880
Over the years,

154
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,160
our Tiandao Palace

155
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,800
in order to suppress the Netherworld,

156
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:56,600
has also lost a considerable number of disciples.

157
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,320
What?

158
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:59,690
Are the Likong clan members precious,

159
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:01,960
while our Tiandao Palace disciples

160
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,320
are worthless?

161
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:04,960
That's not what I meant.

162
00:09:05,040 --> 00:09:06,560
What should we do now?

163
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:20,260
Lanqi Moyuan has half of the Origin Blood in him.

164
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,680
If

165
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:24,340
he volunteers to offer it,

166
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,720
perhaps

167
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:28,240
we won't have to sacrifice a large number of

168
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,170
the Likong Clan.

169
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:33,040
Then let's do it.
